msgid ""
"By The Hollow Voice\n"
"\n"
"Though powerful masters of necromancy can reanimate subjects long dead, most "
"practitioners require a fresh subject. This often means most novices require "
"a subject that has passed no more than three days prior. Attempting to raise "
"minions without the proper knowledge of and training in the necromantic arts "
"can result in an incomplete binding of the soul.\n"
"\n"
"The subsequent breaking of the master and minion relationship can be dire "
"for the hapless novice necromancer."
msgstr ""

